>> source: Joy of Cooking
>> serves: 1/2 cup

Whisk together in a #bowl{} @lemon juice{2%Tbsp}, @white wine vinegar{1%Tbsp}, @honey{1%Tbsp}, @coarse-grain mustard{1%tsp}, and @salt{} and @pepper{} to taste.

Add in a slow, steady stream, whisking constantly @olive oil{6%Tbsp}.

Taste and adjust the seasonings.
